Performance

Class-leading power

Ride on! Pulsar 150 promises performance like none other. Enjoy class-leading 10.3 kW (14 PS) power and enhanced 13.25 Nm torque with our patented DTS-i technology.

Design

Strikingly sporty

Meet the sportiest 150 ever. This bike is loved for its aggressive dagger-edged graphics, carbon fibre accents, and the iconic wolf-eyed headlamp. There's nothing on this icon that goes unnoticed.

Technology

For a thrilling ride

The upright seating position, telescopic front forks and Nitrox rear suspension amplify the thrill of riding a Pulsar.

Safety

Precision & control

Equipped with a 260 mm ventilated front disc brake and ABS technology for ultra-safe braking performance. Ensure stability with a 1320 mm wheelbase & tubeless tyres.
